IF EXISTS ( SELECT * FROM sys.external_tables WHERE object_id = OBJECT_ID('dbo.F_SSTParcelByWaybill') )
    DROP EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.F_SSTParcelByWaybill
GO

CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.F_SSTParcelByWaybill (
	[lms_parcelbywaybill_waybillid] int,
	[lms_parcelbywaybill_aggweight] float,
	[lms_parcelbywaybill_aggchargeweight] numeric(28,2),
	[lms_parcelbywaybill_aggvolweight] float,
	[lms_parcelbywaybill_aggvolumiserweight] numeric(28,2),
	[lms_parcelbywaybill_noparcels] bigint
	)
	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'Semi Structured Data/OPS/sstparcelbywaybill.parquet',
	DATA_SOURCE = [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseParquetFormat]
	)
GO


SELECT TOP 100 * FROM dbo.F_SSTParcelByWaybill
GO
